Example: http://www.autostop.online/

"Let's ride" hitchiking/autostop system

Use-cases:
User can register
-Login/Logout

User can add his vehicle
-User can remove his vehicle
-User can view his vehicles

User can register trip
-User can cancel trip

User can view all trips
-Users can search trips by origin/destination

Users can apply for trip
-User can cancel application for trip
